ygData.messageBody:
I too am Janice in r/l and there was a char named Janice on Bristlebane at
one time. It seemed to odd to stumble across Janice's corpse at every turn.
lol I hope corpses of the same name do not plague your server.


By the way, regarding the subject of "older women" playing EQ, I bet I am
one of oldest. I will be 49 next month. Not that it matters. Maybe it
will give some of you young gals hope that there IS fun after 40. Boy, is
there ever fun after 40.



Janice Too.
